== Urutare rwa Kamegeri ==
Urutare rwa Kamegeri ruherereye muntara yamajyepfo akarere ka Ruhango umurenge wa 
[[Dosiye:Urutare_rwa_Kamegeri_Monument.jpg|thumb|Urutare rwa Kamegeri Monument]]
Ruhango munsi yumuhanda hagati yumujyi wa [[Ruhango (Akarere)|Ruhango]] nahahoze komine Kigoma<ref>https://www.gasabo.net/2018/10/15/amateka-yurutare-rwa-kamegeri-na-ndaba/</ref>

Uru Rutare rwamenyekanye mu mateka yu [[Rwanda Nziza|Rwanda]]  cyane kubera uwo mugabo Kamegeri ba rwitiriye<ref>https://www.rwandagorillatrekking.com/blog/urutare-rwa-kamegeri.html</ref>

Kamegeri yari umutware wumugome kurusha abandi kuko ariwe wazanye icyo gitekerezo cyo gutwikira

umuntu kurutare<ref>https://www.southernprovince.gov.rw/index.php?id=21&L=1</ref> ruherereye mu karere ka Ruhango

== Amateka ==
Urutare rwa Kamegeri nirwo batwikiyeho umutware Kamegeri kuko umwami yaramaze kubona neza ko Kamegeri

umugome kandi umwami atarakundaga guhemuka <ref>https://www.gasabo.net/2018/10/15/amateka-yurutare-rwa-kamegeri-na-ndaba/</ref>

Kamegeri yabayeho kungoma ya Mibambwe II akaba yari umwami uzwiho gukunda abaturage be cyane <ref>http://celebzmagazine.com/menya-imvano-yizina-ryurutare-rwitiriwe-kamegeri-mu-ruhango/</ref> 
[[Dosiye:Rock_of_KAMEGERI.jpg|thumb|AMATEKA Y'URUTARE RWA KAMEGERI]]

== Inkomoko ==
Umwami Mibambwe II Sekarongoro II yasabye abagaragu be ko bashaka igihano cyahabwa umuntu wakoze nabi

bose batangira guhitamo ibihano bitandukanye aribwo umugaragu Kamegeri yagize ati mucanire [[Urutare rwa Ndaba|urutare]] rwature maze mumujugunyreho

[[Umwami|umwam]]<nowiki/>i aherako ariwe abihanisha<ref>https://www.250events.com/ki/menya-amateka-yurutare-rwa-ka-megeri-rusurwa-na-bamucyerarugendo-batandukanye/</ref> kuko yaramenyeneza ko ari umugome

== Ubukera rugendo ==
Urutare rwa Kamegeri ni urutare rusurwa nabatari bake bavuye mugihugu no hanze yacyo 

nka Uganda, [[Tanzaniya]], ndetse na Burundi kubera amateka yarwo

